  "title": "Application Support for AV System (Cisco Webex, O365, Ms Team / Up to $4290)",
  "description": "<p>Seeking for <strong>Application Support for AV System</strong></p><p>1 year contract under agency payroll</p><p><strong>Salary up to $4290 (Company do not provide bonus)</strong></p><p>Work Location: <strong>Changi Business Park</strong></p><p>Working Hours: <strong>Mon to Fri: 9am to 6pm (may require to work after office hour for any urgent issues)</strong></p><p>Requirement:</p><ul><li><strong>Singaporean (must clear client security & pre-employment checks)</strong></li><li><strong>Knowledge in supporting Cisco Webex, Cisco meeting room equipment and Microsoft Teams Room</strong></li><li><strong>Knowledge in Microsoft O365 administration, including SharePoint creation, user administration, mailbox administration</strong></li><li><strong>Advantage if have knowledge in NICE compliance recording</strong></li><li><strong>Experiences in basic troubleshooting and administrative skillsets</strong></li><li><strong>Diploma or Degree in related field</strong></li><li><strong>Would be good to have knowledge in all. However training and guidance will be provided. Most importantly is the willingness to learn.</strong></li></ul><p>ES Recruitment Pte Ltd (09C4235)</p><p>Hong Chiew Guat (R1219860)</p>",
